    <!--My sister is an interesting person whose personality is totally different from mine. She was brought up in
    America, and quite straightforward when dealing with relationships. For e.g. when she has different opinions
    with others, she often voices out her ideas directly, and tries to persuade others with convincing words. While
    as for me, I was raised up in a traditional Chinese family, so under the influence of Chinese culture, I am
